### Product API Examples

### Получить все продукты
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Получить продукт по ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Получить продукты по workflow ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/workflow/workflow-123
Accept: application/json

###

### Создать новый продукт
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mobile App Design",
  "description": "Complete mobile application design with screens and components",
  "totalScreens": 15,
  "totalComponents": 42,
  "workflow": "{\"stages\": [\"design\", \"review\", \"approval\"], \"currentStage\": \"design\"}",
  "workflowId": "workflow-123"
}

###

### Обновить продукт (частичное обновление)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Mobile App Design",
  "totalScreens": 20,
  "totalComponents": 50
}

###

### Обновить продукт (полное обновление)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Complete Mobile App Design",
  "description": "Updated complete mobile application design",
  "totalScreens": 25,
  "totalComponents": 60,
  "workflow": "{\"stages\": [\"design\", \"review\", \"approval\", \"production\"], \"currentStage\": \"review\"}",
  "workflowId": "workflow-456"
}

###

### Удалить продукт
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

###

